# Git Commit
- (start) Status
  - Run: git status
- (validate) Check
  - Check: No .env
  - Check: No debug
  - @validate[1]: OK?
- (type) Type?
  - src/ -> feat/fix
  - tests/ -> test
  - docs/ -> docs
- (scope) Scope?
- (desc) Desc?
- (format) Output
  - Show: <type>(<scope>)!: <desc>
  - Ask: Use?
  - @format[1]: OK?
- Execute: git commit
- End
